title: Trade unions from the media, entertainment and arts sectors in Latin America approve regional charter on fundamental rights and dignity at work
description: During the regional workshop held from 21 to 23 July in Mexico City, trade unions affiliated with FIA-LA and UNI Americas PANARTES approved a charter on fundamental rights and dignity at work in the audiovisual, entertainment and arts sectors in Latin America. This political and union instrument aims to strengthen joint action in response to the challenges facing the sector across the region.
